  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 9.66,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리시"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.66,
      "end": 31.16,
      "text": "영화가 즐거워지는 영어 놀이터 스크린 잉글리시 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.16,
      "end": 33.16,
      "text": "3월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 33.16,
      "end": 36.98,
      "text": "션 시트 감독 핀 릴리틀 주연의"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.98,
      "end": 39.12,
      "text": "스토르 보이입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.12,
      "end": 42.86,
      "text": "드디어 오늘인가요 핀 릴리틀"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.86,
      "end": 45.98,
      "text": "핀 릴리틀 등장 그 시간이 왔습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.98,
      "end": 47.5,
      "text": "너무너무 기대가 됩니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.5,
      "end": 50.56,
      "text": "서민지님께서 인사 나눠주셨는데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.56,
      "end": 53.48,
      "text": "굿모닝 크크크 크리스 샘"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.48,
      "end": 56.78,
      "text": "너무 중독적이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.78,
      "end": 59.84,
      "text": "I like it. Good morning. You made me feel good this morning"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.84,
      "end": 63.8,
      "text": "그렇죠. 너무 에너제릭하게 시작하게 해주셔서 감사드립니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.8,
      "end": 64.82,
      "text": "positive vibes"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.82,
      "end": 65.26,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.26,
      "end": 66.62,
      "text": "positive energy"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.62,
      "end": 69.3,
      "text": "이제 storm boy"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.3,
      "end": 74.64,
      "text": "이 주인공의 목소리를 들을 생각을 하니까 벌써부터 막 positive energy가 넘쳐 흐릅니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.64,
      "end": 78.58,
      "text": "What is it that you like so much about storm boy? You are obsessed"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.58,
      "end": 79.02,
      "text": "adorable"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.02,
      "end": 81.98,
      "text": "정말 제 스타일이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.98,
      "end": 82.42,
      "text": "아 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.6,
      "end": 82.9,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.9,
      "end": 85.78,
      "text": "정말 보고 또 보고 계속 보게 되더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.78,
      "end": 87.1,
      "text": "저도 어릴 때 그랬었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.1,
      "end": 88.56,
      "text": "어릴 때는요"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.56,
      "end": 92.36,
      "text": "I had nice blonde hair and big buck teeth"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.36,
      "end": 94.24,
      "text": "A little gap between my teeth"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.24,
      "end": 96.42,
      "text": "I ran barefoot in the streets"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.42,
      "end": 98.5,
      "text": "어릴 때 사진을 한번 봐야 쓰겄네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.5,
      "end": 98.98,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.98,
      "end": 100.7,
      "text": "I'll prove it"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.7,
      "end": 102.4,
      "text": "자신감에 넘쳐 계시는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.4,
      "end": 103.92,
      "text": "기대되는데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.92,
      "end": 104.9,
      "text": "어쨌든"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.9,
      "end": 110.52,
      "text": "I think this little boy knows how to love nature"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.52,
      "end": 113.06,
      "text": "그리고 love animals"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.06,
      "end": 115.64,
      "text": "이런 것들을 다 알던 소년인 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.64,
      "end": 117.76,
      "text": "He's growing up on the beach"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.76,
      "end": 119.4,
      "text": "with nature, with animals"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.4,
      "end": 119.88,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.88,
      "end": 121.38,
      "text": "Especially the pelicans"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.38,
      "end": 124.7,
      "text": "because this beach is full of pelicans"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.7,
      "end": 125.5,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.5,
      "end": 130.46,
      "text": "이렇게 많은 pelicans들을 한 장소에서 보는 거는 저도 처음인 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.46,
      "end": 131.26,
      "text": "아 저도요"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.26,
      "end": 131.64,
      "text": "그쵸"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.64,
      "end": 132.26,
      "text": "I don't think"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.26,
      "end": 134.68,
      "text": "I don't remember when I saw a pelican in the wild"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.68,
      "end": 136.14,
      "text": "I think I've seen one"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.14,
      "end": 136.46,
      "text": "Have you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.46,
      "end": 136.86,
      "text": "Somewhere"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.86,
      "end": 137.5,
      "text": "진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.66,
      "end": 139.3,
      "text": "I think they have them in the US"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.3,
      "end": 142.1,
      "text": "Minnesota, there's the countryside"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.1,
      "end": 143.9,
      "text": "I've never seen one of them"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.9,
      "end": 144.56,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.7,
      "end": 145.84,
      "text": "Not a single one?"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.94,
      "end": 146.6,
      "text": "한 번도 못 봤어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.6,
      "end": 147.6,
      "text": "Even in the zoo?"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.74,
      "end": 149.86,
      "text": "네, 그냥 저는 다큐멘터리를 통해서만 봐야죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.86,
      "end": 152.1,
      "text": "저는 확실히 봤고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.1,
      "end": 153.18,
      "text": "어디서 봤는지"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.18,
      "end": 153.76,
      "text": "Was it big?"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.18,
      "end": 156.34,
      "text": "It was, you know, average size"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.34,
      "end": 157.56,
      "text": "Average size"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.56,
      "end": 159.32,
      "text": "I saw it catching fish"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.32,
      "end": 159.66,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.66,
      "end": 160.84,
      "text": "With its big beak"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.84,
      "end": 163.9,
      "text": "엄청 중요한 순간을 보셨네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.9,
      "end": 164.68,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.68,
      "end": 165.12,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.12,
      "end": 167.42,
      "text": "네, 그거 착각했으면 좋았을 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.42,
      "end": 169.14,
      "text": "National Geographic"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.14,
      "end": 169.98,
      "text": "Front page"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.98,
      "end": 170.8,
      "text": "Cover page"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.8,
      "end": 172.88,
      "text": "Anyway, Finn Little"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.88,
      "end": 173.84,
      "text": "He actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.84,
      "end": 175.98,
      "text": "To work on this role"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.98,
      "end": 176.34,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.34,
      "end": 178.28,
      "text": "He was introduced to the pelicans"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.28,
      "end": 180.34,
      "text": "When they were only six weeks old"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.34,
      "end": 182.04,
      "text": "So they were little babies"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.04,
      "end": 182.74,
      "text": "Just born"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.74,
      "end": 183.28,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.28,
      "end": 184.68,
      "text": "Tiny little baby pelicans"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.68,
      "end": 187.52,
      "text": "And he would have bonding sessions with them"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.52,
      "end": 188.06,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.06,
      "end": 190.18,
      "text": "So every time"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.18,
      "end": 190.9,
      "text": "Or every week"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.9,
      "end": 191.5,
      "text": "He would go"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.5,
      "end": 192.36,
      "text": "Meet the pelicans"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.36,
      "end": 193.76,
      "text": "And become their friend"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.76,
      "end": 195.12,
      "text": "And they actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.12,
      "end": 196.76,
      "text": "Became really close"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.76,
      "end": 197.44,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.44,
      "end": 198.36,
      "text": "The pelicans to him"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.36,
      "end": 199.2,
      "text": "Him to the pelicans"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.2,
      "end": 200.88,
      "text": "They became best buddies"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.88,
      "end": 203.14,
      "text": "Which really showed in the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.14,
      "end": 205.1,
      "text": "They must have been"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.1,
      "end": 206.56,
      "text": "Like a real family"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.56,
      "end": 209.34,
      "text": "거의 가족과 같지 않을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.34,
      "end": 210.68,
      "text": "As much as a bird"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.68,
      "end": 211.32,
      "text": "And a person"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.32,
      "end": 212.34,
      "text": "Can become family"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.34,
      "end": 213.94,
      "text": "They were buddies"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.94,
      "end": 215.48,
      "text": "왜냐하면 펠리컨들이"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.48,
      "end": 216.72,
      "text": "IQ가 높잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.72,
      "end": 217.38,
      "text": "아"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.38,
      "end": 219.26,
      "text": "그러니까는 약간 가족처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.26,
      "end": 221.46,
      "text": "자기네들도 생각을 하지 않았을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.46,
      "end": 223.78,
      "text": "저도 한번 기대를 해봅니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.78,
      "end": 224.16,
      "text": "IQ"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.16,
      "end": 224.66,
      "text": "IQ"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.66,
      "end": 225.88,
      "text": "몇 시 정도 될까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.32,
      "end": 226.7,
      "text": "그래도"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.7,
      "end": 228.34,
      "text": "Over 80 정도 되지 않을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.34,
      "end": 229.22,
      "text": "예상을 해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.22,
      "end": 229.94,
      "text": "Over 80"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.94,
      "end": 231.48,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.48,
      "end": 232.8,
      "text": "저희 예상이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.8,
      "end": 233.16,
      "text": "Okay"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.16,
      "end": 235.16,
      "text": "That's not too high"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.16,
      "end": 235.8,
      "text": "Too high"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.8,
      "end": 236.22,
      "text": "아 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.38,
      "end": 236.58,
      "text": "그러면"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.58,
      "end": 237.32,
      "text": "Over 90?"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.66,
      "end": 239.1,
      "text": "너무 허한 것 같은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.1,
      "end": 240.06,
      "text": "100 넘은다고 하죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.06,
      "end": 240.32,
      "text": "예?"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.46,
      "end": 241.0,
      "text": "진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.14,
      "end": 241.44,
      "text": "아니요"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.44,
      "end": 242.7,
      "text": "저는 그냥 추적이고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.7,
      "end": 243.58,
      "text": "아 찍으신 거군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.58,
      "end": 244.24,
      "text": "For us"
    },
    {
      "start": 244.24,
      "end": 245.12,
      "text": "Over 100"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.12,
      "end": 246.9,
      "text": "Is good, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.94,
      "end": 247.52,
      "text": "네, 그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.52,
      "end": 248.28,
      "text": "Over 130"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.28,
      "end": 249.6,
      "text": "Is great"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.6,
      "end": 250.16,
      "text": "Genius죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.16,
      "end": 251.14,
      "text": "Genius level"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.14,
      "end": 252.86,
      "text": "I've never had an IQ"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.86,
      "end": 254.28,
      "text": "Have you had an IQ test before?"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.38,
      "end": 254.76,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.76,
      "end": 256.76,
      "text": "하지만 그냥 뭐"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.76,
      "end": 258.2,
      "text": "이야기는 안 하는 걸로"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.2,
      "end": 259.2,
      "text": "아, 네"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.2,
      "end": 260.66,
      "text": "그냥 뭐 노멀합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 260.66,
      "end": 261.38,
      "text": "아, 오케이"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.38,
      "end": 262.26,
      "text": "좋아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.26,
      "end": 262.7,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.7,
      "end": 264.2,
      "text": "오늘 장면 듣고 올게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.2,
      "end": 265.2,
      "text": "Fingerbone"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.2,
      "end": 266.54,
      "text": "He helped me"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.54,
      "end": 268.06,
      "text": "Said he didn't want to come in"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.06,
      "end": 269.88,
      "text": "Said it wasn't right if you went home"
    },
    {
      "start": 269.88,
      "end": 271.26,
      "text": "He's my friend dad"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.26,
      "end": 273.06,
      "text": "He said I had to be like their mom"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.06,
      "end": 274.36,
      "text": "But she piques down their throat"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.36,
      "end": 275.52,
      "text": "I wasn't gonna do that"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.52,
      "end": 276.26,
      "text": "No"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.26,
      "end": 277.46,
      "text": "So I made this"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.46,
      "end": 278.56,
      "text": "Dad, can I keep him?"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.0,
      "end": 279.24,
      "text": "Well"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.24,
      "end": 281.1,
      "text": "The little one looks pretty weak"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.1,
      "end": 282.0,
      "text": "Please"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.0,
      "end": 283.14,
      "text": "I'll look after them good"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.14,
      "end": 285.65,
      "text": "Let's just see how we go"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.65,
      "end": 289.95,
      "text": "할아버지가 되었었던"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.95,
      "end": 292.15,
      "text": "그 마이클 킹니가 아니고"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.15,
      "end": 295.87,
      "text": "이제는 그의 유년 시절로 돌아간 겁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.87,
      "end": 298.15,
      "text": "And there was a huge pain"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.15,
      "end": 300.19,
      "text": "actually in his childhood"
    },
    {
